"{\"uid\": \"straitstimes.com-sport-swimming-us-win-3000th-olympic-medal-but-struggle-for-golds-in-paris-pool\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Choose edition  Search  singapore  asia  world  opinion  life  business  sport  Visual  Podcasts  SPH Rewards  STClassifieds  Paid press releases  Advertise with us  FAQs  Contact us  Sign up now:Get the biggest sports news in your inbox  PublishedJul 31, 2024, 07:09 AM  UpdatedJul 31, 2024, 07:09 AM  PARIS - The United States claimed their 3,000th Olympic medal when Regan Smith and Katharine Berkoff won silver and bronze in the women's 100m backstroke on Tuesday, but they have struggled to reach the top step of the swimming podium at La Defense Arena.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 558, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 98, \"end\": 101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Press_Holdings\", \"score\": 0.9999999998540261, \"rank\": 1.4593444181824539e-10, \"text\": \"SPH\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Press_Holdings\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Press_Holdings\"}, {\"begin\": 147, \"end\": 156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advertise_(horse)\", \"score\": 0.9604822703097123, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Advertise\", \"types\": [\"Q7377\", \"Q729\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advertise_(horse)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advertise_(horse)\"}, {\"begin\": 315, \"end\": 328, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9964107214955715, \"rank\": 0.002343077303563384, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 370, \"end\": 381, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Regan_Smith\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.433220937933584e-21, \"text\": \"Regan Smith\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Regan_Smith\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Regan_Smith\"}, {\"begin\": 386, \"end\": 403, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katharine_Berkoff\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katharine Berkoff\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katharine_Berkoff\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katharine_Berkoff\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While the U.S. have now won 3,000 medals in Summer and Winter Olympics combined, no other country has even half that tally.\", \"from\": 560, \"to\": 683, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But in Paris, the Americans are still well behind in the gold medal charts, with five countries ahead of them - for now.\", \"from\": 685, \"to\": 805, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 692, \"end\": 697, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999915740549, \"rank\": 8.425937813778148e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Australia have won four golds in the pool and although the Americans have won a whopping 15 medals overall, they have claimed only two golds.\", \"from\": 807, \"to\": 948, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 807, \"end\": 816, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9997665114341585, \"rank\": 0.0002117989008155901, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The American men's 4x200m freestyle relay team finished second behind Britain, while Bobby Finke was second in the men's 800m freestyle final on Tuesday night.\", \"from\": 950, \"to\": 1109, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 954, \"end\": 962, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999938380702806, \"rank\": 6.084873245322437e-06, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1020, \"end\": 1027, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9784108007399004, \"rank\": 0.02206549392006598, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1035, \"end\": 1046, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Finke\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bobby Finke\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Finke\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robert_Finke\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think we are always shooting for gold, that's the American standard,\\\" relay swimmer Drew Kibler said.\", \"from\": 1111, \"to\": 1215, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1164, \"end\": 1181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Standard_Companies\", \"score\": 0.9999999519413916, \"rank\": 4.641999782793109e-08, \"text\": \"American standard\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Standard_Companies\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Standard_Companies\"}, {\"begin\": 1198, \"end\": 1209, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Drew_Kibler\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Drew Kibler\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Drew_Kibler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Drew_Kibler\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is a really special thing to be on that podium and it was really tough a few years ago missing that podium.\", \"from\": 1217, \"to\": 1328, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So it's a step forward, but we are always shooting for gold.\\\"\", \"from\": 1329, \"to\": 1390, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"FATHER'S FOOTSTEPS  Exactly 32 years ago to the day, David Berkoff won the men's 100 metres backstroke at the Barcelona Games, and his daughter Katharine followed in her father's footsteps in the women's event in Paris.\", \"from\": 1392, \"to\": 1611, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1445, \"end\": 1458, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Berkoff\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"David Berkoff\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Berkoff\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Berkoff\"}, {\"begin\": 1605, \"end\": 1610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999915740549, \"rank\": 8.425937813778148e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her father won four Olympic medals in all, and when 23-year-old Berkoff won her first, it was also the 600th medal the U.S. had won in swimming.\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1757, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have been dreaming of being at the Olympics for my whole life.\", \"from\": 1759, \"to\": 1824, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I definitely have more goals and I am not quite satisfied yet,\\\" Berkoff told reporters.\", \"from\": 1825, \"to\": 1912, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When asked if her father had given her any advice, she said: \\\"He's been very supportive, just trying to remind me to stay in my own lane, remember why I am doing what I am doing and just do it for myself and no one else.\", \"from\": 1914, \"to\": 2134, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am so grateful they get to be here to watch... just grateful for my parents' support along the way.\\\"\", \"from\": 2136, \"to\": 2239, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Australia's Kaylee McKeown defended her backstroke crown while Americans Smith and Berkoff completed the podium.\", \"from\": 2241, \"to\": 2353, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2241, \"end\": 2250, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9997665114341585, \"rank\": 0.0002117989008155901, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 2253, \"end\": 2267, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaylee_McKeown\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kaylee McKeown\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaylee_McKeown\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaylee_McKeown\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think other people's performances are completely out of my control and Kaylee is one of one.\", \"from\": 2355, \"to\": 2450, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She is an absolutely incredible racer and she knows what to do when it matters,\\\" said Smith after claiming her fourth Olympic medal.\", \"from\": 2451, \"to\": 2583, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am really proud of myself...\", \"from\": 2585, \"to\": 2616, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I stayed in my own lane, I executed my race plan and I left it all in the pool.\\\"\", \"from\": 2617, \"to\": 2697, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"REUTERS  United States  Olympics  Swimming  E-paper  Newsletters  Podcasts  RSS Feed  About Us  Terms & Conditions  Personal Data Protection Notice  Need help?\", \"from\": 2698, \"to\": 2857, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2698, \"end\": 2705, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"REUTERS\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}, {\"begin\": 2707, \"end\": 2720, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9964107214955715, \"rank\": 0.002343077303563384, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2774, \"end\": 2782, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RSS Feed\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reach us here.\", \"from\": 2858, \"to\": 2872, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertise with us\", \"from\": 2874, \"to\": 2891, \"entities\": []}]}"